WEBVTT

00:08:58.530 --> 00:09:04.863
ter menijo, da so njihove skrbi
vredne pozornosti.

00:09:04.863 --> 00:09:06.197
In konec koncev

00:09:06.197 --> 00:09:11.030
cepiva vplivajo na vse 
življenje na planetu.

00:09:11.030 --> 00:09:13.430
Kateri drug zdravstveni ukrep,

00:09:13.463 --> 00:09:15.697
razen vode,

00:09:15.697 --> 00:09:18.863
vpliva na vse?

00:09:18.863 --> 00:09:21.897
Če torej hočete nekaj zmotiti,

00:09:21.930 --> 00:09:23.663
je to popolna tarča.

00:09:24.697 --> 00:09:29.397
Morda moramo zato biti bolj pozorni

00:09:29.430 --> 00:09:32.963
in vrniti zaupanje ljudi v zadeve.